== Isabelle sarah Kabano ==
ni umunyamakuru wa [[Rwanda|Radio Rwanda]] na Radio 10 kugeza mu mwaka wa 2000 yamamaye cyane muri filimi yagiye 

agiramo uruhare Rutandukanye nko gukina nibindi.<ref>https://www.lemonde.fr/afrique/article/2021/07/14/isabelle-kabano-le-rwanda-a-fleur-de-peau_6088271_3212.html</ref> Kabano yavutse mu mwaka wi 1974 avukira mu gihugu 

cy'abaturanyi i [[Uburundi|Burundi]] aho ababyeyi be bari bari mubuhungiro nyuma yaho baje kwimukira i [[Kinshasa]] muri <ref>https://www.lanuitrwandaise.org/isabelle-kabano-le-rwanda-a-fleur,15899.html?lang=fr</ref>

[[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Repuburika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo.]] gusa naho ntago bahatinze kuko baje kwimukira mu mujyi  wa [[Goma|Goma.]]

== Amateka ni mibereho ==
Isabelle Kabano yakuze akunda ibintu bijyanye no gukina amakinamico kuko na papa we umubyara yari umukinnyi<ref>https://www.rfi.fr/fr/podcasts/couleurs-tropicales/20220421-semaine-sp%C3%A9ciale-rwanda-episode-3-avec-isabelle-kabano</ref>

w'ikinamico numuyobozi w'ihuriro ryabakina ikinamico ndetse na Nyina umubyara wari umuririmbyi.nyuma y'urugamaba

rutoroshye rwo Guhagarika [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Genocide yakorewe abatutsi mu Rwanda]] nibwo Kabano numuryango we bafashe icyemezo

cyo kugaruka mu [[Rwanda|Rwanda.]] Kabano kandi yakomeje kwihugura ibijyane nogukina amakinamico mu cyahoze ari 

[[Kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda|Kaminuza nkuru yu Rwanda]] 

== Imirimo ye ==
Kabano nyuma yo kuba umunyamakuru yaje kugirirwa ikizere cyo kuyobora ikinyamakuru cy'ikigo kigihugu RwandAir<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/actress-kabano-speaks-out-her-first-international-award</ref>

Isabelle Kabano yagize uruhare runini mu ma filimi atandukanye harimo nkiyo yakinnye yiswe PETIT PAYS nyuma yo

gusoma igitabo cy'iyonkuru. cy'umwanditsi GAEL FAYE muri 2003 kandi nabwo yagarageye muri filimi bise SHAKE HANDS

ya [[Kanada|RANDOM HOUSE CANADA]]. muri 2005 kandi yagaragaye muyindi filimi bise Iminsi mike muri Mata yakozwe 

n'Abanyamerica bavuga kumateka yakorewe abatutsi muri Mata 1994 nyuma yaho nkimyaka 2 agaragara kandi muri 

filimi bise Zone turquoise ndetse nizindi nyinshi zitandukanye.

== Ibihembo ==
Kabano kandi yagiye atsindira ibihembo byinshi bitandukanye harimo nkicyo yatsindiye cy'umukinnyi mwiza muri <ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2157503/</ref>

film bise petit pays muri fesitivale [[Paris|francophone d'Agoulement i PARIS]] mu [[Ubufaransa|Bufaransa]] kunshuro yayo ya 13 akaba 

ari [[Festival du Cinéma Africain de Khouribga|iserukiramuco]] rya sinema ngarukamwaka ryibanda cyane mukumenyekanisha ama filimi y'igifaransa kuruta ayandi.

kwisi mu bihugu bikoresha [[Igifaransa|ururimi rw'igifaransa.]]<ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/1026862/culture/petit-pays-isabelle-kabano-en-interpretant-yvonne-je-suis-devenue-folle/</ref>

